name: core::num::<impl i16>::strict_pow
doc:
Strict exponentiation. Computes `self.pow(exp)`, panicking if
 overflow occurred.

 # Panics

 ## Overflow behavior

 This function will always panic on overflow, regardless of whether overflow checks are enabled.
